OL,3,CPolice appeal after two people killed
OL,4,Cin car crash
OL,6,FTwo men have been killed in a car
OL,7,Fcrash on Wednesday evening in Kelso.
OL,9,FPolice Scotland officers are now
OL,10,Fappealing for information following
OL,11,Fthe fatal incident.
OL,13,FThe crash occurred at around 6.50pm on
OL,14,FWednesday, April 8, involving a green
OL,15,FFord Fiesta and a silver Nissan Leaf.
OL,17,FBoth of the drivers, who were aged 35
OL,18,Fand 42, were pronounced dead at the
OL,19,Fscene, with no other injuries reported.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/4
