OL,3,CPolice appeal after two people killed
OL,4,Cin car crash
OL,6,FThe incident happened on the Edinburgh
OL,7,FRoad A6089, near the junction for the
OL,8,FB6364.
OL,10,FThe road was closed to allow for
OL,11,Finvestigations, and re-opened the next
OL,12,Fmorning at 1.30am.
OL,14,FSergeant Jamie Humpage said: "Our
OL,15,Fthoughts remain with the family and
OL,16,Ffriends of both the men at this
OL,17,Fextremely difficult time, and our
OL,18,Fenquiries are ongoing to establish the
OL,19,Ffull circumstances of this collision.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/4
