OL,3,CPolice appeal after two people killed
OL,4,Cin car crash
OL,6,F"I am appealing to anyone who was
OL,7,Fdriving in the area at the time or saw
OL,8,Feither vehicle prior to the crash to
OL,9,Fplease come forward and speak with
OL,10,Fofficers.
OL,12,F"I'd also ask that those with dash-cam
OL,13,Ffootage or CCTV please review this to
OL,14,Fsee if it has captured anything that
OL,15,Fcould assist with our investigation."
OL,17,FAnyone with information is asked to
OL,18,Fcontact Police Scotland on 101,
OL,19,Fquoting incident number 2926 of 8
OL,20,FApril, 2026.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/4
